const Forms = () => { const [firstBoxValue, setFirstBoxValue] = useState(""); const handleFirstBoxChange = (event) => { setFirstBoxValue(event.target.value); }; const [formData, setFormData] = useState({ Nomination: "", Category: "", FirstName: "", LastName: "", Address: "", City: "", JobTitle: "", Phone: "", StreetAddress: "", codeZip: "", email: "", Organization: "", SubCategory:"", }); const handleForm = (e) => { setFormData({ ...formData, [e.target.name]: e.target.value, }); }; // console.log("object",formData) const handleSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); // Create an object to hold the form data const data = { Nomination: formData.Nomination, Category: formData.Category, FirstName: formData.FirstName, LastName: formData.LastName, SubCategory:formData.SubCategory, Address: formData.Address, City: formData.City, JobTitle: formData.JobTitle, Phone: formData.Phone, StreetAddress: formData.StreetAddress, codeZip: formData.codeZip, email: formData.email, Organization: formData.Organization, }; axios .post("https://gla-backend-new-dt4z.onrender.com/awardForm", data) .then((response) => { console.log(response.data); }) .catch((error) => { console.error(error); }); }; return ( {/* Place the component you want to center here */}
